      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained executive sedan that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Midnight Blue metallic that still catches the light beautifully; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the cabin features premium cream leather upholstery that has been treated regularly to maintain its soft texture, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the high-fidelity sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound and ready for the road. It comes with a complete service portfolio, showing consistent oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake pad replacement. The engine runs smoothly without any hesitation, and the automatic transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining on the original alloy wheels. This is an honest, well-cared-for car looking for its next long-term owner.",
